{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.480", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben es gerade geh\u00f6rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD ist nicht nur rassistisch und nationalistisch,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.120", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.400", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie ist auch militaristisch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.440", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bundeswehreinsatz in Mali ist mit rund 1\u00a0000\u00a0Soldatinnen und Soldaten neben dem Afghanistan-Einsatz der derzeit gr\u00f6\u00dfte Auslandseinsatz \u00fcberhaupt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.441", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.441", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht bei dem Einsatz nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.520", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es den Menschen vor Ort geht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.480", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielmehr reiht sich der Einsatz ein in eine Reihe von Ma\u00dfnahmen zur Abwehr von Fl\u00fcchtlingen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.720", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen soll die Bundeswehr auch unter schwierigen klimatischen Bedingungen die weltweite Einsatz- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.720", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Kampfbereitschaft erproben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.920", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niels Annen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.000", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist schon ein bisschen zum Piepen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.600", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundesregierung von Frankreich gezwungen worden w\u00e4re, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in diesen Einsatz zu gehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beides, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.120", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sowohl die Fl\u00fcchtlingsabwehr als auch diese \u00fcbergeordneten Ziele der Bundeswehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.121", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lehnt Die Linke ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.121", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.320", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut Mandat sollen die Bundeswehrsoldaten im Rahmen der UN-Mission MINUSMA den Frieden sichern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.321", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch in Mali gibt es mitnichten Frieden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.321", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens haben gar nicht alle Konfliktparteien das ausgehandelte Friedensabkommen unterzeichnet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zweitens flankieren die MINUSMA und damit auch die Bundeswehr eine Kampfoperation der franz\u00f6sischen Armee, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Dunkeln agiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.520", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gelegentlich kommt ans Tageslicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.080", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie diese Operation unter dem Namen Barkhane agiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.081", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im letzten Jahr kam es zu Protesten der Zivilbev\u00f6lkerung in Kidal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nachdem die franz\u00f6sische Armee Menschen willk\u00fcrlich verhaftet hatte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.400", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "MINUSMA-Soldaten schossen auf sie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor sechs Wochen kam es zu erneuten Protesten von ganzen Familien gegen die Operation Barkhane. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.080", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr darf nicht Teil einer Milit\u00e4rmission sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in Mali wie eine koloniale Fremdmacht agiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.280", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung stellt mit der Heron-Drohne\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hat die Ministerin auch noch einmal erkl\u00e4rt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aufkl\u00e4rungsbilder zur Verf\u00fcgung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte wissen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.080", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wird mit diesen Bildern alles gemacht?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.680", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich gebe einmal ein Beispiel: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor einem Monat sind bei einem Bombardement durch die franz\u00f6sische Armee elf malische Soldaten get\u00f6tet worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.200", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist \u00fcbrigens nur bekannt geworden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.680", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es sich dabei um verb\u00fcndete Soldaten handelte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch wie viele Zivilisten sind bei vergleichbaren Bombardements umgekommen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.280", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber schweigen sich die Regierungen in Paris und Berlin aus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.160", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Mali wie in Frankreich wird die Kritik an dem internationalen Milit\u00e4reinsatz immer lauter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die franz\u00f6sische Tageszeitung \u201eLe Monde\u201c schrieb dazu letzte Woche: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mali ist unser Afghanistan.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.320", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn die Aktionen westlicher Milit\u00e4rs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.321", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Armut und die Korruption der vom Westen gest\u00fctzten Regierung in Bamako treiben den Aufst\u00e4ndischen immer neue Unterst\u00fctzer zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.321", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.360", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun sind auch Regionen in den Nachbarl\u00e4ndern Niger und Burkina Faso betroffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und im Landesinneren von Mali ist ein v\u00f6llig neuer bewaffneter Konflikt entstanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.720", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Unsicherheit und der Krieg weiten sich aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.721", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich richte meine Worte hier an die gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrende Bundesregierung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.721", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.722", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nehmen Sie diese Realit\u00e4t zur Kenntnis!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.722", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.723", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der internationale Milit\u00e4reinsatz bringt den Menschen vor Ort nichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.723", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.724", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deren gr\u00f6\u00dftes Problem ist die bittere Armut\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.724", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.725", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "trotz des Reichtums an Bodensch\u00e4tzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.725", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.726", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die WHO hat gerade gemeldet: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.726", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.727", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Mali stirbt jede Stunde ein Kind unter f\u00fcnf Jahren an Lungenentz\u00fcndung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.727", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.728", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt alle Mittel auf die Beseitigung der Armut und der Ursachen des Konfliktes zu setzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.728", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.729", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "steckt die Bundesregierung mal eben 6,5\u00a0Millionen Euro in eine Webserie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.729", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.730", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die fl\u00e4chendeckend in ganz Deutschland f\u00fcr den Milit\u00e4reinsatz in Mali wirbt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.730", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.731", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.731", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.732", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stecken Sie die Millionen nicht in eine Reklame, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.732", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.733", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eine Realit\u00e4t vorgaukelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.733", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.734", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dieser Einsatz nicht hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.734", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.735", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6ren Sie auf damit! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.735", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.736", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr muss umgehend aus Mali abgezogen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.736", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.737", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke wird gegen dieses Mandat stimmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.737", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.738", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.738", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner ist der Kollege Frithjof Schmidt von der Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen."
   ]
  }
 ]
}